org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.resourcemanager.reservation.planning

Class TryManyReservationAgents

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.resourcemanager.reservation.planning.TryManyReservationAgents
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ReservationAgent

    public class TryManyReservationAgents
extends Object
implements ReservationAgent
    A planning algorithm that invokes several other planning algorithms according to a given order. If one of the planners succeeds, the allocation it generates is returned.
